<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 20:06:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>法国马克龙称彻底摧毁哈马斯需要10年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/frances-macron-says-total-destruction-of-hamas-will-take-10-years/0000018c-2b97-d04a-af9f-fbb78cc40000</link><description>法国总统在迪拜举行的 COP28 气候峰会上发表讲话，敦促以色列明确其对哈马斯的目标。他说：“如果以色列的安全是以巴勒斯坦人的生命为代价来实现的，那么以色列在该地区就不会有持久的安全。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 18:06:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/frances-macron-says-total-destruction-of-hamas-will-take-10-years/0000018c-2b97-d04a-af9f-fbb78cc40000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯释放的以色列人质在特拉维夫集会上发表讲话，数千人呼吁立即释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-released-from-hamas-captivity-set-to-speak-at-tel-aviv-rally/0000018c-2b69-d04a-af9f-fbfb66e90000</link><description>以色列各地举行集会，要求释放剩余人质。除了特拉维夫的主要集会外，海法和凯撒利亚也举行了示威活动，要求达成另一项人质协议并驱逐内塔尼亚胡</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 17:22:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-released-from-hamas-captivity-set-to-speak-at-tel-aviv-rally/0000018c-2b69-d04a-af9f-fbfb66e90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称，自 10 月 7 日起失踪的 Ron Binyamin 被绑架到加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-ron-binyamin-declared-missing-since-oct-7-was-kidnapped-into-gaza/0000018c-2b1f-d04a-af9f-fbbf3a620000</link><description>这位来自雷霍沃特的 53 岁丈夫和两个孩子的父亲于 10 月 7 日与朋友一起骑自行车旅行，然后失踪了。同样在周六，以色列军队宣布加沙师南部旅指挥官阿萨夫·哈米上校死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 17:07:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-ron-binyamin-declared-missing-since-oct-7-was-kidnapped-into-gaza/0000018c-2b1f-d04a-af9f-fbbf3a620000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日大屠杀八周后，联合国妇女署谴责哈马斯对以色列妇女使用性暴力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/after-eight-weeks-un-women-condemns-hamas-use-of-sexual-violence-on-oct-7/0000018c-2b09-dc03-a9ec-3f7ba0190000</link><description>在 10 月 13 日首次发表声明谴责对以色列平民的袭击之后，联合国妇女署关于这场战争及其对妇女影响的所有公开评论都只集中在巴勒斯坦人身上。它在推特上发布了一份谴责哈马斯上周袭击事件的声明，然后又删除了</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 16:43:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/after-eight-weeks-un-women-condemns-hamas-use-of-sexual-violence-on-oct-7/0000018c-2b09-dc03-a9ec-3f7ba0190000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德负责人回忆卡塔尔停火调解小组：“哈马斯没有履行协议中的部分内容”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/mossad-chief-recalls-team-from-qatar-hamas-did-not-fulfill-its-part-of-the-deal/0000018c-2ade-d5f2-a5cc-6edebe620000</link><description>哈马斯周五未能提供商定的加沙以色列妇女名单，而是试图将尸体包括在内。卡塔尔的以色列调解小组整个周末都在继续谈判，但周六决定召回他们</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 16:12:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/mossad-chief-recalls-team-from-qatar-hamas-did-not-fulfill-its-part-of-the-deal/0000018c-2ade-d5f2-a5cc-6edebe620000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯裔以色列男子在以色列北部的车内被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-man-shot-dead-in-his-car-in-northern-israel/0000018c-2ae1-d04a-af9f-faf327710000</link><description>这名 50 岁的男子被确认为阿贝德·马卡尔达 (Abed Makalda)。这是以色列北部阿拉伯城市同一周内发生的第三起谋杀案，2023 年以色列-阿拉伯犯罪浪潮因加沙战争而放缓</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 15:16:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-man-shot-dead-in-his-car-in-northern-israel/0000018c-2ae1-d04a-af9f-faf327710000</guid></item><item><title>国际刑事法院检察官首次访问以色列：“有理由相信”哈马斯在 10 月 7 日犯下了战争罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/icc-prosecutor-in-first-ever-israel-visit-reason-to-believe-hamas-committed-war-crimes/0000018c-2a67-d5f2-a5cc-6e7798c80000</link><description>国际刑事法院首席检察官汗表示，他的办公室将很乐意与以色列合作调查 10 月 7 日的事件，并且不会阻止他进行调查，即使以色列维持目前不承认法院管辖权和不合作的政策用它</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 14:38:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/icc-prosecutor-in-first-ever-israel-visit-reason-to-believe-hamas-committed-war-crimes/0000018c-2a67-d5f2-a5cc-6e7798c80000</guid></item><item><title>为拯救纳哈尔·奥兹而奋战并倒下的以色列国防军观察气球操作员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/the-idf-observation-balloon-operators-that-fought-and-fell-to-save-nahal-oz/0000018c-29ab-db3a-a1be-3dffe8db0000</link><description>五名以色列士兵成功击毙了入侵其前哨基地的哈马斯特种部队的几名恐怖分子，但在 10 月 7 日的战斗中阵亡。气球失灵等系统性军事失败以及对以色列国防军高层警告的无视，导致了这场悲剧</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 10:08:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article/.premium/the-idf-observation-balloon-operators-that-fought-and-fell-to-save-nahal-oz/0000018c-29ab-db3a-a1be-3dffe8db0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯：只有释放所有巴勒斯坦囚犯才能额外释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article-live/heavy-rocket-fire-to-central-israel-deaths-of-six-hostages-held-by-hamas-confirmed/0000018c-288c-d04a-af9f-f8bec8c60000</link><description>以色列国防军一夜之间袭击了加沙 400 多个目标，其中包括南部城市汗尤尼斯 ■ 加沙卫生官员：自周五上午休战结束以来，已有 184 人死亡 ■ 黎巴嫩火灾后以色列限制北部社区的行动 ■ 报道称以色列告诉阿拉伯国家它希望建立缓冲区战后加沙 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀；加沙仍有超过 159 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：加沙至少有 15,200 人死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 03:32:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article-live/heavy-rocket-fire-to-central-israel-deaths-of-six-hostages-held-by-hamas-confirmed/0000018c-288c-d04a-af9f-f8bec8c60000</guid></item><item><title>“10 月 7 日之后，多层次的创伤正在影响以色列人。它具有传染性”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/there-is-a-multilayered-trauma-taking-place-in-the-wake-of-october-7-its-infectious/0000018c-2774-d04a-af9f-f7f6ddf30000</link><description>一位权威专家表示，即使是没有亲身经历哈马斯袭击的人也可能会出现创伤症状</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 00:17:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/there-is-a-multilayered-trauma-taking-place-in-the-wake-of-october-7-its-infectious/0000018c-2774-d04a-af9f-f7f6ddf30000</guid></item><item><title>当加沙战争肆虐时，以色列军队和定居者在拉马拉感到高兴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-12-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/while-war-rages-in-gaza-israeli-troops-and-settlers-grow-trigger-happy-in-ramallah/0000018c-26f0-db3a-a1be-37fff7a70000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，已有 31 名巴勒斯坦人在拉马拉地区被士兵杀害，有时还被定居者杀害</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 22:15:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-12-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/while-war-rages-in-gaza-israeli-troops-and-settlers-grow-trigger-happy-in-ramallah/0000018c-26f0-db3a-a1be-37fff7a70000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战事重燃加剧了以色列人质家人的恐惧和愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/renewal-of-gaza-fighting-heightens-fear-and-anger-for-israeli-hostages-families/0000018c-26fe-d5f2-a5cc-66fea43b0000</link><description>加沙仍有136名人质被扣押，他们的家人呼吁政府尽一切努力释放人质，并表达了对红十字会的愤怒</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 21:35:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/renewal-of-gaza-fighting-heightens-fear-and-anger-for-israeli-hostages-families/0000018c-26fe-d5f2-a5cc-66fea43b0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争？内塔尼亚胡正忙着纠缠媒体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/war-in-gaza-netanyahu-is-busy-badgering-the-media/0000018c-2654-d5f2-a5cc-6654997a0000</link><description>他正试图让他的福克斯新闻版在安息日播出，并提出两项会侵蚀新闻自由的法案。不管怎样，甚至他的许多支持者也表示，他应对以色列当前的灾难负责</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 21:15:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/war-in-gaza-netanyahu-is-busy-badgering-the-media/0000018c-2654-d5f2-a5cc-6654997a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡是最后一个能够使加沙去激进化的人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-the-last-person-who-could-de-radicalize-gaza/0000018c-2689-d5f2-a5cc-669d2a500000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡非常清楚如何使民众变得激进。像乔治·W·布什一样，他助长了当地的激进主义，并通过占领赋予其合法性</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 20:38:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-the-last-person-who-could-de-radicalize-gaza/0000018c-2689-d5f2-a5cc-669d2a500000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯扣押的六名人质证实在囚禁中被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/six-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-confirmed-killed-in-captivity/0000018c-251a-dc03-a9ec-3d7baab00000</link><description>以色列军方证实10月7日被哈马斯绑架的六名以色列公民死亡：其中包括一名幼儿园教师、一名牧场主和一名退休农民</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 20:16:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/six-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-confirmed-killed-in-captivity/0000018c-251a-dc03-a9ec-3d7baab00000</guid></item><item><title>我是以色列军事情报局的心理学家。这就是为什么单位总是出错的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-was-a-psychologist-at-israels-military-intelligence-heres-what-its-doing-wrong/0000018c-26c2-d04a-af9f-f6f2b8500000</link><description>当我被军事情报局聘用时，我被告知他们对我在跨文化心理学方面的工作感兴趣。我发现的是一个身体，它被自己的内部文化所束缚，以至于它无法倾听相反的声音</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 19:51:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-was-a-psychologist-at-israels-military-intelligence-heres-what-its-doing-wrong/0000018c-26c2-d04a-af9f-f6f2b8500000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列通知阿拉伯国家，希望在战后加沙建立缓冲区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/israel-informs-arab-states-it-wants-buffer-zone-in-postwar-gaza-sources-say/0000018c-268e-d04a-af9f-f6be18c70000</link><description>据地区安全官员称，缓冲区的目的是防止未来的袭击，作为加沙非军事化计划的一部分。美国官员重申，他们“不会支持缩小加沙的地理限制”</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 19:10:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/israel-informs-arab-states-it-wants-buffer-zone-in-postwar-gaza-sources-say/0000018c-268e-d04a-af9f-f6be18c70000</guid></item><item><title>应对恐怖袭击期间杀害平民的以色列士兵：我们开枪直到他们倒下</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-who-killed-civilian-during-response-to-attack-we-shot-until-they-fell/0000018c-25c7-dc03-a9ec-3dff4f720000</link><description>辛贝特、警方和宪兵正在调查一名以色列平民的死亡事件。枪杀他的士兵告诉电视采访者，“每个士兵都渴望检查这个盒子”</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 16:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-who-killed-civilian-during-response-to-attack-we-shot-until-they-fell/0000018c-25c7-dc03-a9ec-3dff4f720000</guid></item><item><title>以色列著名政治学家、杰出犹太复国主义学者什洛莫·阿维内里 (Shlomo Avineri) 去世，享年 90 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/shlomo-avineri-renowned-israeli-political-scientist-eminent-zionist-scholar-dies-at-90/0000018c-2540-d04a-af9f-f5f2c9e60000</link><description>阿维内里是世界上最重要的马克思和黑格尔著作、犹太复国主义和社会主义研究者之一，也是一位多产的作家和记者。他对西方民主国家面临的挑战提出警告，称“我们仍未成功找到应对这些挑战的工具”</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 12:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/shlomo-avineri-renowned-israeli-political-scientist-eminent-zionist-scholar-dies-at-90/0000018c-2540-d04a-af9f-f5f2c9e60000</guid></item><item><title>“他们被下了药”：被释放的以色列人质的亲属讲述哈马斯被囚禁的恐怖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/they-were-drugged-relatives-of-freed-israeli-hostages-channel-hamas-captivity-horror/0000018c-24c7-dc03-a9ec-3cff21210000</link><description>一名兽医正在对枪伤进行手术；一名八岁的孩子在枪林弹雨中挨家挨户跑；一位母亲不知道她三岁的女儿是死是活。随着人质返回以色列，哈马斯被囚禁的证词浮出水面</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 10:16:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-01/ty-article/.premium/they-were-drugged-relatives-of-freed-israeli-hostages-channel-hamas-captivity-horror/0000018c-24c7-dc03-a9ec-3cff21210000</guid></item></channel></rss>